{"heading":"David praises God as his defense, his rock, and his salvation—The Lord judges men according to their works.","number":62,"verseCount":12,"verses":[[1,["Truly my soul waiteth upon God: from him ",["cometh",["clarity-word"]]," my salvation."]],[2,["He only ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," my rock and my ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]],"; ",["he is",["clarity-word"]]," my defence; I shall not be greatly moved."]],[3,["How long will ye imagine mischief against a man? ye shall be slain all of you: as a bowing wall ",["shall ye be, and as",["clarity-word"]]," a tottering fence."]],[4,["They only consult to cast ",["him",["clarity-word"]]," down from his excellency: they delight in lies: they bless with their mouth, but they ",["curse",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Curse","tg/curse"],"."]]]," inwardly. ",["Selah",["selah"]],"."]],[5,["My soul, wait thou only upon God; for my expectation ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," from him."]],[6,["He only ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," my ",["rock",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Rock","tg/rock"],"."]]]," and my salvation: ",["he is",["clarity-word"]]," my defence; I shall not be moved."]],[7,["In God ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," my salvation and my ",["glory",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Glory","tg/glory"],"."]]],": the rock of my strength, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," my ",["refuge",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Refuge","tg/refuge"],"."]]],", ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," in God."]],[8,[["Trust",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Trust in God","tg/trust-in-god"],"."]]]," in him at all times; ye people, pour out your heart before him: God ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," a refuge for us. ",["Selah",["selah"]],"."]],[9,["Surely men of low degree ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," vanity, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," men of high degree ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," a lie: to be laid in the balance, they ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," altogether ",["lighter",["clarity-word"]]," than ",["vanity",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Vanity","tg/vanity"],"."]]],"."]],[10,["Trust not in ",["oppression",["study-note-ref","a",["OR extortion."]]],", and become not vain in robbery: if ",["riches",["study-note-ref","b",[["Job 31:25","ot/job/31.25"],"; ",["Luke 12:15","nt/luke/12.15"],"; ",["Alma 5:53 (53–56)","bofm/alma/5.53"],"; ",["Hel. 12:2 (1–5)","bofm/hel/12.2"],"; ",["D&C 56:16 (16–18)","dc-testament/dc/56.16"],"."]]]," increase, set not your ",["heart",["study-note-ref","c",[["Jacob 2:19 (18–19)","bofm/jacob/2.19"],"."]]]," ",["upon them.",["clarity-word"]]]],[11,["God hath spoken once; twice have I heard this; that power ",["belongeth",["clarity-word"]]," unto God."]],[12,["Also unto thee, O Lord, ",["belongeth",["clarity-word"]]," ",["mercy",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 86:15","ot/ps/86.15"],"."]]],": for thou renderest to every man according to his ",["work",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Good Works","tg/good-works"],"; ",["Justice","tg/justice"],"."]]],"."]]],"volume":"ot"}